{
  "stem": "3666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mom, too-- no, my mom worked harder work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think my mom worked, I think shoving coals in a big oven.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would-- she didn't think she would survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, very difficult, but if not so my mom and my aunt, I would not be alive because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when we got to Stutthof, after Riga, again, if not for my aunt and my mother, I would not be alive today.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Different places.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think my aunt maybe worked with me, and the advantage there was that we did come in contact with Gentile.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is Riga.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whereas previously we didn't come in contact with any Christians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in this factory, we did come in contact with some Christians, and sometimes they would hand me a little piece of bread, me and another of my friend, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would hand the kids an extra few bites of bread or maybe a piece of sugar or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They felt pity for us, but that was-- that was a help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very helpful because we were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I only dreamed of having a loaf of bread so I can finish the whole loaf all by myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we were very hungry and very thin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My feeling was that I envied the existence of a dog.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I wanted to be a dog so I would be cared for, so I would have this little doghouse, and nobody would bother me and even feed me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just couldn't understand in any sense how I am responsible for such a situation and why the Germans hated the Jews so much.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't understand this at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, more or less.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
